caption:
Ok, this is my ship request that I said I’ll send in and it’s for all of your ship. Now because you know me I’ll just add that I’m a Leo and ENFJ (which you already knew too) and if you want me to add a short description I can, just message me Delphie. Also, just do it when you feel like it, this is sort of like a reminder post and if you want, I can send them in with like 3 groups each.

So the groups: BTS, Got7, Nct, iKON, Stray Kids, Monsta X, Seventeen, Vixx and Pentagon (so basically all of them😂😂😂😂😂)

P.S. I’m making a special request because I want you to ship me with who you think I’ll suit in SUJU and KNK. I want your honest opinion, so can I request this as a friend???? Your completely your choice!!!!!!!!!

—

OKAY CHEN HERE IT COMES, I FINALLY DID IT SO PREPARE. This is 100% my true, honest opinion.

BTS

Don’t ask me why but I’d ship you with Jin. He seems like the type that’ll make you laugh till your stomach hurts. Also based on appearance, I think he’s the one who’ll fit you the most.

GOT7

Even if he weren’t your bias, it would’ve been him. Period.

NCT

I dON’T EVEN KNOW WHY BUT IT HAS TO BE LUKE-

iKON

I’ve been thinking about it lately, and the two of you would match so damn good??? Like damn girl, you sure he isn’t your bias?

STRAY KIDS

He’s just so cute and that’s also why you two would be great together x

MONSTA X

Maybe not appearance that much, but I think your personalities fit surprisingly well.

SEVENTEEN

I don’t even have an explanation for this, but ??? This seems about right…

VIXX

You two match definitely, appearance-wise (unfortunately I don’t know him well enough to judge on personality)

PENTAGON

BECAUSE YOU FIT HIM  P E R F E C T L Y. I can’t believe I didn’t notice that until now??

KNK

I’m gonna stick to the one I shipped you with in the first place, Heejun.


Prepare yourself for the last one.

-

-

-

SUPER JUNIOR

I’M SORRY CHEN BUT I COULDN’T BRING MYSELF TO SHIP YOU WITH ANYONE OTHER THAN HYUKJAE. THANKS TO YOU I GOT TO KNOW HIM AND HIS AMAZING 4D PERSONALITY AND I CAN’T SEE YOU BEING WITH ANYONE ELSE, LET ALONE FROM SUJU. YOUR PERSONALITIES FIT SO WELL. AND APPEARANCE TOO, HE JUST MATCHES YOU IN EVERY ASPECT. HE’S YOUR HUSBAND AND I GIVE YOU MY BLESSING. Delph out.

—

Note: I usually don’t do this many groups. Chen being one of my dearest mutuals, I’d love to make an exception for her.

summary: It's okay, it doesn't matter anymore (Game on)
title: It's okay, it doesn't matter anymore (Game on)
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2MjBK8T

by Kookspantythief

“I’m kinda busy with my song and I kind of need that file right now so I can finish my work. Where are you anyways?”

“NO! You have to help me, Yoongs.. My life is depending on it, the sake of the universe depending on you.” pleaded Hoseok, his voice was already in verge of crying, which made both Yoongi and Jungkook to frown. Yoongi rolled his eyes, shifting in his seat.

“Okay, okay, chill. What is exactly the thing you needed my help with?”

“I need you to babysit my bother.”

And there was a loud silence.

“HELL NO. I’m hanging up-”

“I need you to babysit my bother.”

And there was a loud silence.

“HELL NO. I’m hanging up-”

body:
The Heirs of Bangtan pt. 3

This series isn’t turning out so bad. Like, it’s mostly out of context, but the aesthetic is like 45% there so it’s all good.

Namjoon | Seokjin | Yoongi | Hoseok | Jimin | Taehyung | Jungkook

The Indifferent Instrumentalist

Min Yoongi

  • he’s cold both internally and externally
  • the only time you’d find him “warm” if if he’s playing the piano next to he fire place in winter
  • the kingdom of Bangtan barely sNOWS tHOUGH
  • o-O
  • alright
  • so he’s kinda closed off and doesn’t like to interact with people much
  • but it is not due to shyness
  • no no sIR
  • he’s just very blunt
  • and he is aware of that so he takes into consideration how others might feel
  • most of the time
  • but the rest of the time he doesn’t give a flyin flup
  • there’s this music room in the castle where he spends most of his time in anyways if not inside his room composing
  • expect random outbursts
  • random random outbursts of just anything really
  • like a word, phrase, whatever comes to his head
  • he is not as intimidating as he may seem, but he’s still intimidating
  • you may rarely see him out of his room as he may either be conposing, or sleeping
  • or a combination no fckin clue how that works but okay
  • now he is the type of ruler who is on top of things
  • yeah he’ll be crash, harsh, and stoic but it keeps the face that he is damn serious about important matter
  • the scariest thing about him is that he is not afraid to hurt people in order to get his way
  • he won’t feel any remorse for them, not even for his own brothers (depending on the situation)
  • if it is a situation that can be handled without placing harm to his brothers but to others…
  • he would take that risk
  • he is actually quite protective of his family though it may not show
  • he believes it exhibits a weakness others can use to their advantage on him
  • he keeps that hidden as well as his actions to protect them
  • overall, he’s not a bad guy
  • he is an aloof man who doesn’t give a flying shet about life and does his best to get by
  • if he kingdom is in his hands, however
  • you bet he’ll make it the best
  • “Frankly, I do not care what you think, if that was not obvious enough. Just don’t get in my way.”

Mas agora, eu vou esquecer sobre você

 Isso vai ser menos doloroso 

Do que continuar te culpando


Eu tento afastar o você que me faz sentir frio por dentro 

Como fumaça, uma fumaça branca 

Eu digo que vou te apagar 

Mas honestamente, eu ainda não posso te deixar partir”
